ber of kinks in\nterms of the normalized participation ratio of initial states in the eigenbasis\nof the interacting Hamiltonian.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Feb 2022 18:22:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Feb 2022 12:50:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 12 Jun 2022 14:30:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-14"}
