peratures in Na$_2$Cu$_2$TeO$_6$,\nbut also for the universality of the strongly correlated state in a broad range\nof quantum magnetic systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Feb 2022 06:02:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-14"}
