 elastic interactions. By accessing\ntime-dependent atomic correlations in energy materials, we resolve the\nlong-standing disagreement between local and average structure probes, and show\nthat spontaneous anisotropy is ubiquitous in cubic IV-VI materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Feb 2022 11:51:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 May 2023 07:07:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-26"}
