\\mathcal{N}=4$ super Yang-Mills appears to predict the maximal weight terms of\nthe planar pure Yang-Mills all-plus amplitude. We test this relationship for\nthe two-loop $n$-point Yang-Mills amplitude, as well as for the three-loop\nfour-point amplitude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Feb 2022 13:29:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-14"}
