hin single observations. We find long-term changes in the energy\ndistribution, the average spectrum, and the sad-trombone drift, compared to\nearlier and later published observations. Despite the large burst rate, we find\nno strict short-term periodicity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Feb 2022 15:42:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Jan 2023 18:35:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-09"}
